<a href="#" name="1"></a>
<b><u>1. Top Status Bar</u></b> - <a href="#top">Top</a><br />
The stats on the top of the screen show your gang tags and your username (example: [Mod] SpecialOps0). Below that it shows your current level, under that it shows how much money you currently have outside of the bank. Under that it says bank which is a clickable to deposit money and next to that it shows how much money is in your bank currently. Below that it shows how many points you have, under that is how many credits you have. The use option takes you to a page where you can spend your points and the buy option takes you to the page where you can spend $USD to buy in game items).<br />
On the right hand side on the top are images of your current stats. This displays your current HP, energy, awake, nerve, and experience. If you hover over the bar it will show how much you have, out of how much your max currently is. The more green the bar is the better.<br /><br />
<a href="#" name="2"></a>
<b><u>2. The Home/Index Page</u></b> - <a href="#top">Top</a><br />
The Home button contains a lot of useful information. Under General Information it shows your name, your level, your cash, your cash in your bank, your current experience (with an exp guide), marijuana, HP, energy, awake, nerve, work EXP, and GCSEs. They are all displayed in numbers for ease.<br />
Below that is Attributes, all this does is tell your current strength, speed, defense, and total stats.<br />
Next up is Modded Attributes, this shows your current stats with the percentage your weapon, armor, and shoes add on to them.<br />
Under that is your Battle Stats, showing how many battles you've won, lost, the total added together of win and loss and how much money you've gained, or lost from killing people.<br />
Crime Stats; this shows how many crimes you have succeeded, failed, the total of them and how much money you've made off of crimes.<br />
Daily Statistics show how many kills you've had today and how much EXP you've gained today. This will reset to 0 each day for you to train back up and show it.<br />
Next up is My Badges, which is a link to view your badges. Badges are just awards for various things that have been done in the game itself.<br /><br />
<a href="#" name="3"></a>
<b><u>3. The Updates List</u></b> - <a href="#top">Top</a><br />
This is a list of what is currently being updated or what will be updated if known in advance by the staff and will be beneficial for you to check it out to see what is happening in game.<br /><br />
<a href="#" name="4"></a>
<b><u>4. Inventory</u></b> - <a href="#top">Top</a><br />
Your inventory shows items that you currently own. It also shows your equipped weapon, armor and shoes. From your inventory you can control your items by selling them, marketing them, equipping them. You can only have 250 items max, in your inventory at one time.<br /><br />
<a href="#" name="5"></a>
<b><u>5. Your City</u></b> - <a href="#top">Top</a><br />
This is a very important option to use. You will click this nearly the most in the entire game. You can do countless options from this menu. This clickable brings up over 20 options to choose from as well as showing today's top hitman with how many kills and the top exp gainer with how much.<br /><ul type="disc">
