    <li>The armour store allows you to buy armor for a set amount of cash, the item market again will be a better deal always check there.<br />
    <li>The shoes market will allow you to buy shoes at a set amount of cash, the item market is a better deal.<br />
    <li>The point shop allows you to refill your nerve, and energy for 10 points, it will refill awake for 1 point every %, you can also sell 5 points for 5k if you are in desperate need, however I'm sure others will gladly buy them for a lot more.<br />
